first_time_on_tubi.title: First Time on Tubi

100002855.description: Twins Essie and Ella are best friends who share a passion for gymnastics. When they are both up for the same event, its causes a divided, and they're faced with the challenge of competing against each other.

100002858.title: Summer With the Guys
100002858.description: Four college football players lose their scholarships and become strippers over the summer to make money to go back to school in the fall.

100002869.title: Battle of the Gods
100002869.description: Two Viking Gods and sworn enemies fall through a ripple in space time and find themselves in the present day world. Only a young girl, unaware if her powers can find the portal and bring them back.

100002870.title: The Standard
100002870.description: Ten special forces combat veterans and fifty civilians converge on Jacksonville Beach, for what is considered to be the toughest endurance event in the world. At 48+ hours and 80+ miles, the pass rate for participants is less than 2%. Inspired by Special Forces training, the event is not only a way to test ones mettle, but its also an attempt to bridge the military-civilian divide. It is a roller coaster of emotions for both the candidates and the cadre.

100002872.title: The Place of No Words
100002872.description: A young boy battles the complexities of a grown-up world with his father.

100002915.title: Vanity Vixens
100002915.description: When Assante discovers their longtime girlfriend Tierra is cheating on him, his life begins to spiral downward. His best friend Ced introduces him to Vanity Vixens, an agency that specializes in helping tormented lovers get the revenge they desire.

100002917.title: The Tipping Point
100002917.description: Vice captain Cheng Rui (Zhou Yiwei) tracked down the bizarre fall of female college students, only to find that the case involved such underworld crimes as loan arbitrage, violent extortion and entrepreneur An Yiming (Zeng Zhiwei). What is the future?

100002919.title: The Unnaturals
100002919.description: Five people take refuge from a howling storm in a forgotten inn owned by a strange man and his clairvoyant mother, discovering during a séance the others' depths of depravity.

100002921.title: Ballad of Billy Badass
100002921.description: Our Story follows mobster Billy Badass as he tries to make a better life for himself. Unfortunately, the only way he can do so is if he kills the competition and takes control. Will he succeed or die trying?

100002922.title: Bigfoot Files 1: Sightings in the Pacific Northwest
100002922.description: Bigfoot, also known as Sasquatch, is a legendary creature said to inhabit the forests and wilderness areas of North America, particularly in the Pacific Northwest region of the United States and Canada. Join us, as we explore the mythos of Bigfoot.

100002924.title: Return of the Witch
100002924.description: When an archaeological team unearths a body and removes a wooden stake from it, the corpse turns into a living, beautiful naked woman, whom the villagers regard with fear as an ancient witch returned to life.

100002928.title: Connie
100002928.description: A preteen girl experiences demonic encounters involving her sister, Connie. However, not believing her accusations, Laycie is looked at as being eccentric, overly hormonal and an attention seeker, but is there really something more?

100002930.title: Ninja in the Mafia's Shadow
100002930.description: The film follows a ninja named Lee, who works as a pizza delivery guy in the day. The mafia has taken over the pizzeria that he works at and is charging too high of rent. It is up to Lee to go take on the mafia and save the pizzeria.

100002933.title: Ocean
100002933.description: Best friends Cindy and Lori spend a vacation on the Gulf Coast. Their serene trip becomes a nightmare when they find themselves alone at sea.

100002934.title: Paladin Crossworlds
100002934.description: Giant robots like Metal Angels, people who communicate directly with the mind without a word, improve people who dominate fields of energy, mind, and strength, a code to open the hidden doors of DNA and thus discover the secrets of Space and Time.

100002939.title: Trappn 2 Rappn 2
100002939.description: When trying to make an honest living doesn't work, Darts gets caught up in credit card scams and the dark side that comes with it, going from the swipe life to the rap life.

100002943.title: Watch Your Six
100002943.description: A homicide detective must navigate questionable suspects and police corruption to solve the murder of a seemingly dirty cop.

100002944.title: Honeymoon Horror
100002944.description: A romantic getaway turns into a Honeymoon from Hell when a prudish couple checks into a sexy retreat haunted by a demonic serial killer in this gritty homage to ‘80s shot-on-video horror movies.

100002945.title: Malaysia’s Last Tigers
100002945.description: Journey to the rainforests of Malaysia to meet the elusive Malayan tiger and discover what efforts are taking place to protect this striped hunter from extinction.

100002946.title: Code Name: Dynastud
100002946.description: In the year 2024, homosexuality has been outlawed by an extreme right-wing government. Only one extraordinary man can stop this wave of terror and repression, a superhero for our troubled times.

100002947.title: The Chant of July
100002947.description: Chemistry student Jane Thunder abuses a synthetic drug with terrifying results.

100002948.title: The King of Arcades
100002948.description: This critically acclaimed documentary follows arcade owner and punk rockstar Richie Knucklez as he creates one of the biggest arcade phenomena in the world. Follow the rise and fall of the King of Arcades as one man pursues his dream against all odds.

100002951.title: Frontier Sumatra
100002951.description: This documentary tells the incredible story of Restorasi Ekosistem Riau (RER), a ground-breaking rainforest conservation project in the Kampar Peninsula of Sumatra.

100002952.title: Jon Benét's Tricycle
100002952.description: A unique individual who collects almost everything reveals some of the darker things he has acquired, including Jon Benet Ramsey's tricycle. An investigation of pop culture, media, tragedy and the items we possess.

100002956.title: Searching for Sasquatch: Extended Edition
100002956.description: Jason ventures into the dark forests of B.C. Canada searching for the legendary creature known as Sasquatch. Sasquatch, in Canadian and American folklore, is an ape-like creature that inhabits forests of North America. Now in an Extended Edition.

100002957.title: How Earth Was Formed
100002957.description: This documentary explains, how the Earth was formed, from the very beginning of the solar system, to present day.

100002960.title: Stay Out of the Basement
100002960.description: Mackenzie is hired to babysit for a lonely young girl named Peyton, only to discover a sinister presence may be lurking within the house.

100002961.title: Mister Creep
100002961.description: Three college students stumble upon a secret television broadcast of a clown-faced serial killer and search for its location.

100002962.title: The Platinum Pussycat
100002962.description: With $100,000 at stake and gangsters on their trail, Dena and her ex-lover Baron must outwit, outrun and outshoot their way out of Cleveland in this groovy mashup of spy, crime, and noir genres!

100002965.title: Cobra Strike Force
100002965.description: In the year 2028 the Los Angeles Police have been defunded, so it's up to the Cobra Strike Force to rescue the Employees of the LA Plaza during a hostage situation involving the notorious Viper Gang.

100002969.title: Dirty Third 2: Home Sweet Home
100002969.description: Hip-hop stars Scarface, E-40, Big Pokey, and Lil Troy are featured in this down-and-dirty look at the rap music scene in Houston, Texas. The Dirty Third 2: Home Sweet Home also features guest appearances from funnymen Reynaldo Rey and Rodney Winfield.

100002970.title: Doomed: Hunter S. Thompson's American Dream
100002970.description: Doomed: Hunter S. Thompson’s American Dream is a documentary that focuses on famed American writer, political activist, and creator of Gonzo Journalism, the late Dr. Hunter S. Thompson.

100002972.title: Revenge of the First Wives
100002972.description: A city faces ruin against the ruthless acts of Mafia boss Don Carlo. The latest casualties in this war: 3 undercover cops. The mayor and police department seem defeated until new allies emerge, the widows of the slain officers.

100002978.title: Pussie Control: The Story of Davion Pussie
100002978.description: Davion Pussie is a hood cat with a tight bond with his owner, Tiana. When Tiana dates a new man, who isn't who he appears to be, Davion warns her of his advances. Can Davion get to the bottom of his intentions before it spells disaster for him and Tiana?

100002979.title: Book of Creatures
100002979.description: Four horror stories filled with Creatures, Critters and other Creepy things sure to chill your bones!

100002980.title: Santorini Blue
100002980.description: A New York to Santorini, Greece story about rekindling the spark for love, creativity & life!

100002981.title: FP3: Escape From Bako
100002981.description: JTRO and Fam embark on their most dangerous mission yet: Forcing them to battle foes from the past in order to save their future from a calamity that threatens to wipe humanity off the mo' suckin' face of the Earf...4EVZ.

100002983.title: Creek
100002983.description: Bobbie ventures out on her kayak, while her friend Connor sets up camp in the woods. She discovers something along the creek that sets her on the run for her life.

100002985.title: Me Her Her
100002985.description: A bourgeois couple experiences boredom after a few years of marriage, and in this case boredom in the bedroom.

100002989.title: Tutti Frutti
100002989.description: Roma, 1959. In a luxurious apartment in the Trieste neighborhood, a very beautiful woman named Belle de Jour entertains her influential clients

100002990.title: The Professor
100002990.description: Roberta seduces her art history professor into a trap at his home. The story of an extreme night will lead us to know sad and erotic weaknesses.

100003024.title: Worth the Price
100003024.description: An ex-Navy Seal will stop at nothing to rescue his sister from her abductors and exact revenge.

100003033.title: La Historia De La Semana Santa (Doblado)
100003033.description: La Historia de la Semana Santa cautivará a los niños a medida que aprenden sobre el amor de Dios a través de la vida y el ministerio milagroso de Jesús.

100003034.title: La Historia De Navidad (Doblado)
100003034.description: Acompaña a la oruga Garabato a un viaje súper interesante, y conoce la emocionante historia que culmina con el nacimiento Jesús.

100003037.title: Schoolgirl Hitchhikers
100003037.description: Two female hitch-hikers get mixed up with a gang of thieves and their stolen jewelry.

0300000222.title: Wrestling Reality
0300000222.description:
Wrestling With Reality body slams the viewer into the action of the real people behind the characters of a fiercely passionate group of professional wrestlers: the Kardinal Sinners. We follow them on a make-or-break tour, which will either allow them to control their destiny or tear them apart.
This series lays bare the entertaining reality of pro-wrestling and makes viewers regret ever saying that wrestling is fake.

0300000197.title: A Woman of Independent Means
0300000197.description: Follows seven decades of love, loss and courage in the life of a member of Dallas’ high society through her two marriages, three children and beyond.

0300000020.title: She's Still Not Our Sister
0300000020.description: After their father's death, three sisters adjust to having a newly-discovered half sister and the realization that an inheritance can't buy happiness.

0300000204.title: The Pure and the Damned
0300000204.description: The life of Donnie Ferrari and his time in the mafia is portrayed, while his son, Abel Ferrari, tries to outshine his father's shadow at any cost.

0300000193.title: The Mind of a Chef
0300000193.description: Anthony Bourdain takes viewers on a fascinating culinary journey, as he delves into the minds of the world’s best chefs and restaurateurs.

0300009773.title: Frontier Doctor
0300009773.description: This series follows the adventures of Dr. Bill Baxter, a small-town doctor working in the Arizona territory during the early 1900s.

0300000175.title: Bishop & Chainey
0300000175.description: A mission turns deadly as the FBI tracks an elusive criminal with connections to high ranking-officials in the department.

0300000157.title: Bike World
0300000157.description: This series brings viewers the latest action and all that is new in the high-octane world of motorcycles—on-road, off-road, or on-track.
